Constant Field Values

APPEND_DROP_ACCURACY_MARGIN

public static final int APPEND_DROP_ACCURACY_MARGIN
If a Drop is performed when the mouse is on a TreeItem T but near of its top, GXT interprets it as an insert (as the previous sibling of T) instead of an append (as child of T). This constant defines this margin, in pixels.
